          <a
            href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/"
            class="text-cinnabar-700 hover:text-cinnabar-600 hover:line-through"
            >LICENSE</a
          > (Changed model position)
        </li>
        <li>
          Noto Color Emoji Font: Google - <a
            href="https://scripts.sil.org/cms/scripts/page.php?site_id=nrsi&id=OFL"
            class="text-cinnabar-700 hover:text-cinnabar-600 hover:line-through"
            >LICENSE</a
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          Playfair Display Font: Claus Eggers Sørensen - <a
